<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link964593" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=964593&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F1679416-injustice-anywhere-is-a-threat-to-justice%2Fanswers%2F964593-yes-in-king-s-letter">flag</a>
</div>
