<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/53121662-jesus-and-john-wayne"><img alt="Jesus and John Wayne: How White Evangelicals Corrupted a Faith and Fractured a Nation" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1611376522l/53121662._SX98_.jpg" />
